@startuml
title IterLife Reunion 文章发布异步处理流程图
autonumber "<b>[000]"

skinparam Shadowing false
skinparam sequence {
  ParticipantPadding 16
  BoxPadding 10
  ArrowThickness 1
  LifeLineBorderColor #6B7280
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ParticipantBorderColor #475569
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  GroupBorderColor #94A3B8
  GroupBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
}

box "GitHub 侧" #FFF8E1
  participant "GitHub Webhook" as GitHubWebhook
  participant "GitHub API" as GitHubApi
end box

box "IterLife Reunion 系统" #E3F2FD
  participant "WebhookController\nWebhook 接收器" as WebhookController
  participant "ArticlePublishEventService\n发布事件服务" as PublishEventService
  participant "ArticlePublishEventRepository\n发布事件仓储" as PublishEventRepo
  participant "publishEventTaskExecutor\n发布线程池" as PublishExecutor
  participant "Recovery Scheduler\n恢复调度器" as RecoveryScheduler
  participant "ArticleSyncService\n文章同步服务" as SyncService
  participant "ArticleFrontmatterService\nFrontMatter 处理服务" as FrontmatterService
  participant "ArticlePublishEventItemRepository\n发布事件文件项仓储" as PublishEventItemRepo
  participant "ArticleFrontmatterRepository\nFrontMatter 状态仓储" as FrontmatterRepo
  participant "ArticleRepository\n文章仓储" as ArticleRepository
  participant "MeilisearchIndexService\n搜索索引服务" as MeiliService
end box

note over PublishEventService, PublishExecutor
代码事实：
1. webhook 验签成功后先写 article_publish_event
2. 使用显式 ThreadPoolTaskExecutor 作为发布线程池
3. 定时扫描 RECEIVED / RETRY_READY / stale in-flight 事件
end note

note over WebhookController, MeiliService
当前流程边界：
1. 202 Accepted 仅表示系统已接单，不表示文章已完成投影
2. deliveryId、event status、file item status 已落库
3. 仍缺少后台事件查询 / 重试 / 回放 API
4. DB 投影与 Meili 仍是最终一致
end note

== 异步投递 ==

GitHubWebhook -> WebhookController: 发送 webhook 请求
WebhookController -> PublishEventService: 验签后接收事件
PublishEventService -> PublishEventRepo: insert RECEIVED
PublishEventService -> PublishEventRepo: mark DISPATCHING
PublishEventService -> PublishExecutor: 提交 eventId
WebhookController --> GitHubWebhook: 202 Accepted(eventId)

note over WebhookController, PublishExecutor
现状：
GitHub 侧拿到的是 accepted 状态；
真正的文件发现、正文拉取、FrontMatter 处理与投影仍在后台继续执行。
end note

alt 任务提交成功？否
  PublishExecutor --> PublishEventService: 拒绝执行 / 运行时失败
  PublishEventService -> PublishEventRepo: mark RETRY_READY + next_retry_at
else task submitted
  PublishExecutor -> SyncService ++: processPersistedEvent(eventId)
end

== 进程内执行 ==

SyncService -> SyncService: 收集路径并开始批次处理
note over SyncService
单次 push 的 changed / removed 文件数量没有显式上限，
批次越大，内存、耗时和外部 API 压力越大。
end note

alt commits[] file list missing
  SyncService -> GitHubApi: 调用 compare API
  GitHubApi --> SyncService: CompareChanges
  note over SyncService, GitHubApi
  compare API 失败时仍需要依赖事件级重试或后续运维补偿，
  当前还没有专门的 compare 子阶段重试编排。
  end note
end

loop for each changed file
  SyncService -> GitHubApi: 调用 contents API 拉取正文
  alt 正文拉取失败
    GitHubApi --> SyncService: 空结果 / 错误
    SyncService -> PublishEventItemRepo: 标记 item=FAILED
    note over SyncService
    单文件失败已可追踪，
    但尚无自动文件级重试 / 手工重试 API。
    end note
  else contents fetch success
    GitHubApi --> SyncService: 返回 markdown 与 sha
    SyncService -> FrontmatterService: 执行 normalizeChangedFilesIfNeeded(...)

    alt 需要 bot 回写
      FrontmatterService -> FrontmatterRepo: 插入 PENDING 指纹记录
      alt 首次出现该 fingerprint
        FrontmatterRepo --> FrontmatterService: PENDING 已插入
        FrontmatterService -> GitHubApi: PUT 规范化后的 Markdown
        alt bot 回写成功
          GitHubApi --> FrontmatterService: 返回 commit sha
          FrontmatterService -> FrontmatterRepo: 标记为 NORMALIZED
          FrontmatterService --> SyncService: replayDeferred++
          note over FrontmatterService, FrontmatterRepo
          当前补偿策略仍主要依赖 GitHub 因 bot commit 触发新的 replay push，
          后续可补“超时未 replay 时主动补投影”。
          end note
        else bot 回写失败
          GitHubApi --> FrontmatterService: 失败
          FrontmatterService -> FrontmatterRepo: 标记为 FAILED
          FrontmatterService --> SyncService: 回退为进程内直接投影
        end
      else fingerprint already exists
        FrontmatterRepo --> FrontmatterService: 返回 PENDING / FAILED / NORMALIZED
        note over FrontmatterService
        当前已具备的局部幂等：
        通过 fingerprint 防重复提交、识别 replay、
        并对 FAILED 提供 markPendingForRetry。
        end note
      end
    else 不需要 bot 回写
      FrontmatterService --> SyncService: 直接透传
    end

    SyncService -> ArticleRepository: upsertArticleWithMappings(meta)
    ArticleRepository --> SyncService: 数据库已更新
    SyncService -> MeiliService: upsert 搜索索引
    note over SyncService, MeiliService
    article 投影和 Meili 同步不是统一事务。
    DB 成功、Meili 失败时，会出现短暂或长期索引不一致。
    end note
  end
end

== 恢复与补偿边界 ==

RecoveryScheduler -> PublishEventRepo: 扫描 RECEIVED / RETRY_READY / stale in-flight
PublishEventRepo --> RecoveryScheduler: 返回待恢复事件
RecoveryScheduler -> PublishEventService: 重新分发 eventId

alt 异步任务执行完成
  SyncService -> SyncService: 记录最终统计
else 仍存在失败 item / 失败 event
  SyncService -> PublishEventRepo: 更新 FAILED / PARTIAL_FAILED / RETRY_READY
  note over PublishEventRepo
  剩余短板：
  仍缺少面向运维的事件详情、手工重试、回放与索引重建 API。
  end note
end

@enduml
